  "title": "Business Development Specialist (Export)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a Singapore‑based fastener manufacturer and solutions provider specializing in high‑performance fastening products for the construction, oil & gas, and industrial sectors. Due to their current expansion plan, they are looking for Export Business Development to join their team, in hopes of developing the current high performing team. They are located at North.</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><ul><li><strong>Sales Planning & Targeting</strong> – Set, communicate, and monitor sales objectives, quotas, and forecasts for territories.</li><li><strong>Revenue & Profit Management</strong> – Project sales volume and profits, establish pricing, and achieve/exceed sales and profit targets.</li><li><strong>Sales Strategy & Execution</strong> – Develop, implement, and review field sales action plans for national sales or distributors.</li><li><strong>Team Management</strong> – Recruit, train, guide, and evaluate national sales staff or distributor performance.</li><li><strong>Customer Relationship Management</strong> – Build, maintain, and expand the customer base while servicing existing clients.</li><li><strong>Professional Development & Collaboration</strong> – Stay updated on industry trends, participate in networks, and contribute to team objectives.</li></ul></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 5 years’ of relevant experience</li><li>Possess Regional / Channel Management experience</li><li>Possess B2B experience (no retail)</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p>Email: <strong>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</p><p>EA License No. 19C9682</p><p>EA Reg. No. R23115141 (Tan Su Yee)</p>",
